sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Controller<br/>(Shelly Pro 4PM)
    participant P as Pump<br/>(Wilo Z20/4)
    participant VT as V_top<br/>(3-way)
    participant VI as V_pump_in<br/>(3-way)
    participant VO as V_pump_out<br/>(3-way)
    participant FS as Flow Sensor
    participant COL as Collectors

    Note over C: T_outdoor < 2°C detected
    C->>P: Stop pump
    P-->>C: Pump OFF confirmed

    Note over C: Wait for pump to fully stop
    C->>VT: Switch to position B (air intake)
    C->>VI: Switch to position B (collector bottom)
    C->>VO: Switch to position B (to tank)
    VT-->>C: Valve switched
    VI-->>C: Valve switched
    VO-->>C: Valve switched

    Note over C: All valves in drain position
    C->>P: Start pump

    loop Monitor flow
        FS-->>C: Flow detected (water)
        Note over COL: Water pumped out,<br/>air entering from top
    end

    FS-->>C: Flow = 0 (empty)
    C->>P: Stop pump
    Note over C: Collectors drained successfully
